  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nTalk to an expert\nStart free trial\nBacklinks API\n\nAccess detailed and trustworthy backlink data that’s scalable, export-ready, and ready to use.\n\nAPI access is included in every SE Ranking plan\n\nTalk to an expert\nExplore documentation\nComplete backlink data and metrics from one of the industry’s largest crawlers\nRich backlink data you can trust\n\nSE Ranking’s Backlink API pulls sources from one of the web’s most active crawlers. It uses over 15 key backlink metrics at once to help with link quality analysis, competitor strategy tracking, backlink profile building, and more.\n\nBacklink count: \n\n The target’s total number of backlinks\n\nReferring domains: \n\n Individual websites that link to your target\n\nAnchor texts: \n\n See the text people use to link to you\n\nLink types: \n\n Dofollow/nofollow, text/image links, href, redirects, etc.\n\nAuthority scores: \n\n InLink Rank (page authority) and Domain InLink Rank (domain authority)\n\nReferring IPs and subnets: \n\n Network-level link diversity data linking to a target\n\nTop countries and TLDs: \n\n Geographic breakdown of your link profile\n\nAnd more!\n\nScalable & flexible integration\n\nThis Backlink API is built to handle big jobs with ease:\n\nStream up to 100,000 backlinks per call using cursor-based pagination\n\nExport full datasets as compressed CSVs for in-depth analysis\n\nPick the exact analysis level you need: domain, host, or URL\n\nReal-time backlink monitoring & historical data tracking\n\nStay on top of changes with daily updates:\n\nNew/lost link tracking: \n\n Explore the links you gained or lost on the specified date\n\nHistorical trends: \n\n Dive deep into the history of new and lost backlinks and referring domains, including specific reasons for lost links (like page not found, link removed, redirect changes, etc.)\n\nUse filters to distill data by link status, date range, or authority scores\n\nMassive backlink cover",
